#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "1. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Nandiyasutta"
msgstr "10. With Nandiya"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.10:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho nandiyo paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the wanderer Nandiya went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "sn45.10:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho nandiyo paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side, and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn45.10:1.4"
msgid ""
"“kati nu kho, bho gotama, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbānaṅgamā honti "
"nibbānaparāyanā nibbānapariyosānā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, how many things, when developed and cultivated, have "
"extinguishment as their culmination, destination, and end?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhime kho, nandiya, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbānaṅgamā honti "
"nibbānaparāyanā nibbānapariyosānā."
msgstr ""
"“These eight things, when developed and cultivated, have extinguishment as "
"their culmination, destination, and end."

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.3"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"They are: right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right "
"livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, nandiya, aṭṭha dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbānaṅgamā honti "
"nibbānaparāyanā nibbānapariyosānā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These eight things, when developed and cultivated, have extinguishment as "
"their culmination, destination, and end.”"

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.5"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, nandiyo paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, the wanderer Nandiya said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.6"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.7"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.9"
msgid "Avijjāvaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.1"
msgid "Avijjañca upaḍḍhañca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.2"
msgid "sāriputto ca brāhmaṇo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.3"
msgid "Kimatthiyo ca dve bhikkhū,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.4"
msgid "vibhaṅgo sūkanandiyāti."
msgstr ""
